    {
      "reviewerId": null,
      "reviewerUrl": null,
      "name": null,
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 12,
      "isLocalGuide": false,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "Justlife管理的非常好,很乾净, 工作人员都被训練的很好, 也很有爱心, 把需要照料的家人安排在这里可以非常放心，衷心的推荐。\n非常感谢Justlife工作人员对我爸爸这七个月来悉心的照料。特别感谢Ms Pang及Rene,她们真的非常细心及有爱心👍",
      "textTranslated": "Justlife is very well-managed and clean. The staff are well-trained and very caring. I feel very reassured leaving family members who need care here. I highly recommend it.\n\nI am very grateful to the Justlife staff for their excellent care of my father over the past seven months. Special thanks to Ms. Pang and Rene; they were truly very attentive and loving. 👍",
      "publishAt": "2 years ago",
      "publishedAtDate": "2023-08-22T01:49:53.292Z",
      "likesCount": 2,
      "reviewId": "ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURwanNYZTN3RRAB",
