      "responseFromOwnerDate": "2024-10-07T03:01:56.000Z",
      "responseFromOwnerText": "Thank you for sharing such a positive experience and take your precious time to write such an awesome review. We deeply appreciate your review and it truly motivates us to continue to serve the elderly with all we can.",
      "reviewImageUrls": [],
