    },
    {
      "reviewerId": null,
      "reviewerUrl": null,
      "name": null,
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 12,
      "isLocalGuide": false,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "我要感谢Justlife 的全体员工对我父亲细心的照顾。我的父亲因肠胃问题住了一个月的医院。出院之后身体非常虚弱也无法自理，而且对饮食有严格的要求，不然会再次刺激伤口。负责人也很及时的为家人们提供我父亲身体的情况，也在食物上按照我们的意思去准备，一点也不马虎。这里的环境也相当好，能够给于我父亲一个宁静的环境，让他可以好好休养。在经过一个月的细心照顾下，我父亲的慢慢恢复了，也能够达到可以自理的情况。我父亲也跟我反映员工们都很照顾他，他很感激。",
      "textTranslated": "I want to thank all the staff at Justlife for their meticulous care of my father. He was hospitalized for a month due to gastrointestinal issues. After being discharged, he was very weak and unable to care for himself, and had strict dietary requirements to avoid further aggravating his wounds. The staff at Justlife promptly provided my family with updates on my father's condition and prepared his meals according to our preferences, without any carelessness. The environment here was also excellent, providing my father with a peaceful space to recuperate. After a month of attentive care, my father gradually recovered and was able to care for himself again. My father also told me that he was very grateful for the staff's kindness.",
